<h4>Rat's tail</h4>
<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 col-sm-8">
    One of the ingredients, a Rat's tail, can only be obtained as a drop from rats. The archery shop has plenty of rats, which can be defeated using recoil, poison or TFK.
